channel.title: The Titan has fallen!
channel.description:
That's rights gents. The GT Titan is officially only the second best. The 780 TI recently came out and has dethroned the titan. What's even better is that the card is $300 less than the titan.
http://www.newegg.com/Product/Product.aspx?gclid=CObor4Gg8boCFabm7AodoBIAng&Item=N82E16814127771&nm_mc=KNC-GoogleAdwords&cm_mmc=KNC-GoogleAdwords-_-pla-_-Desktop+Graphics+Cards-_-N82E16814127771&ef_id=UoPRfAAAALhMwUtl:20131119161728:s
I hear Gigabyte has an amazing cooler on theirs as well.
